item.title: Adrian Martinez left Nebraska.. for better or for worse?
item.description: Nebraska football had another tough season and Adrian Martinez was on the front lines of the hate being received. He has now transferred to play at Kansas State, making many Husker fans appreciative, but was he really the issue? Let’s take a look. Nebraska had multiple offensive players suffer injuries throughout the season, leaving Martinez as the Huskers’s biggest threat. His rushing yards are high and his passing yards… not so high.
